{"tid":230861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[道德撚] 建構「敬少/幼」理論","createTime":"2017-05-05T15:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T12:49:58.000Z","uid":114175,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e703549b840d4a657a2a164dcc3194a9a1338704","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"香港以至世界各地嘅社會主流意見都傾向敬老,，究其原因無非都係要迫新一代分享應得嘅社會資源，令佢地嘅餘生可以過得安逸。<br />\n<br />\n但大家有冇諗過「敬老」依個觀念背後理據有幾充分?<br />\n<br />\n我地先假定每個人都係有自由意志(free will) 去做任何佢地想做嘅事，包括了結自己嘅生命。但每個人都有一件事係違背(against)佢地嘅free will，個件事就係「出生」，或者話係「被生育」。被父母帶黎依個世界嘅時候，佢地係絕對冇可能先咨詢你嘅意見，所以無論你係想嚟抑或唔想嚟，你都係無得揀。<br />\n<br />\n係以上前提下，每個被生出嚟嘅人，其實都應該受上一代人尊敬，因為佢地嘅出現，係上一代人任性嘅結果(因為無可能尊重被生育者嘅意願，所以點都會係一個任性嘅決定)。如果係咁，「敬老」嘅理念根本站不住腳，因為由始至終，上一代都一定係對唔住下一代。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係反對人生育，亦無可能咁做，因為人類嘅最基本存在意義就係繁殖。但若果依個繁殖嘅決定係唔可能理性，係咪應該做返個氣氛去compensate 「被生育者」呢?<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好TLDR，因為我地依一代都有責任，為下一代做返d嘢，彌補返佢地被生出嚟嘅不幸..."},{"pid":"993a7af91c1bcd6d7e712d8e566c5893cf76a9e3","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c7cf8fad17c2c746edcd62d5b3006388af0199","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e1541fb86fd7e15f001ed01def77e9d67c70ad","tid":230861,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263ae90d252e33d2efcd9f20deba633a9c897509","tid":230861,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"連登咁多低質小學雞，你自推到出年都冇乜人理你ed正經po架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edeeeffccf6673384ea6f7b905e56ad895515e7","tid":230861,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"btw，整體上同意，除左e句 &ldquo;因為人類嘅最基本存在意義就係繁殖。&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48f5736c183f21be28e5cb5802b3c19d9563222","tid":230861,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得就算生<br />\n都要有能力俾到良好生活(甚至一世)佢為前題<br />\n而佢選擇自殺 都要尊重佢決定<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔諗住生"},{"pid":"c2753cdc1d437fd4c52e46c8d7957e56a865a7c2","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登咁多低質小學雞，你自推到出年都冇乜人理你ed正經po架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明呀，咪一人講多兩句嗌醒佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c8506442c5e3a1007059ca452226cabe5a52db","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得就算生<br />\n都要有能力俾到良好生活(甚至一世)佢為前題<br />\n而佢選擇自殺 都要尊重佢決定<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔諗住生</blockquote><br />\n絕對認同呀，但都有子非魚嘅問題，因為even移左民諗比到好嘅將來佢，都係我地嘅一廂情願"},{"pid":"ed05439f4adff569a2924d0b6aef09b2bdeba5b0","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw，整體上同意，除左e句 &ldquo;因為人類嘅最基本存在意義就係繁殖。&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過google reproduction being an unethical act, 但出黎嘅都係d講試管嬰兒係咪不道德, 所以我先諗係咪因為生育係人類嘅基本使命, 所以學術先唔敢討論生育係咪對下一代不道德囉"},{"pid":"9eb126db63090427ea99b29ed06aef9284bdc50f","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba001f602838593d3f9b41f76d7ba973b319ca1","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640e42cf557c10156074bf5f8039397a07d8af1a","tid":230861,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你個post太正經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbae29be97355cbc3bf130d65127e28487f6d7c4","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你個post太正經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但比廢老壓迫得太耐想為其他人諗下一條出路"},{"pid":"6b835baacc33d52535caa84febc382de99b69162","tid":230861,"uid":19730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"we cannot always build the future for our youth but we can build our youth for the future<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcafcc786a9d52714d552928b8b46555579105f","tid":230861,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw，整體上同意，除左e句 &ldquo;因為人類嘅最基本存在意義就係繁殖。&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生物最根本目的其實就係繁衍後代<br />\n等自己嘅物種可以一直維持落去唔好滅絕&amp;擴大勢力(姐係佔有資源充足/適合生存嘅環境等等)<br />\n就算係人類都一樣姐"},{"pid":"6708823e404947309cba8ab9c7473022e0a9a41d","tid":230861,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"換個角度諗<br />\n班老嘅一樣係非自願情況下被生出黎<br />\n但佢地(多數)都曾經為社會作出貢獻<br />\n依個係咪就係敬老站得住腳嘅原因呢<br />\n<br />\n講番轉頭<br />\n尊重尊敬其實都應該係針對一個人本身<br />\n而唔係一個年齡層"},{"pid":"94b84f8dad4daa8db7f8ce417a8c67353df4265d","tid":230861,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你個post太正經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但比廢老壓迫得太耐想為其他人諗下一條出路</blockquote><br />\n呢類思想由發表，出現至盛行？真係隨時以百年計<br />\n尤其是 華人又千年儒家文化之類 根深蒂固"},{"pid":"8eccb6475a2d8e2079b6f8c04dd1d51e6f570a16","tid":230861,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換個角度諗<br />\n班老嘅一樣係非自願情況下被生出黎<br />\n但佢地(多數)都曾經為社會作出貢獻<br />\n依個係咪就係敬老站得住腳嘅原因呢<br />\n<br />\n講番轉頭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">尊重尊敬其實都應該係針對一個人本身<br />\n而唔係一個年齡層</span></blockquote><br />\n紅字十分認同"},{"pid":"0e2774f9c86994f4b792a05e5b34779573d33c54","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換個角度諗<br />\n班老嘅一樣係非自願情況下被生出黎<br />\n但佢地(多數)都曾經為社會作出貢獻<br />\n依個係咪就係敬老站得住腳嘅原因呢<br />\n<br />\n講番轉頭<br />\n尊重尊敬其實都應該係針對一個人本身<br />\n而唔係一個年齡層</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但依個循環總要有一代「老人」犧牲，令下一代人唔洗再被自己壓迫囉<br />\n<br />\n人類社會係喜歡將概念generalize ，咁先容易消化嘛"},{"pid":"9776db707a86d71124aefb70fc4cbfdfe49d42c7","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78129882c30409092e40ecd934e971e81dfb51e","tid":230861,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"我認為free will 嘅存在本身已經compensate咗被生育哩樣嘢。<br />\n<br />\nfree will 嘅存在係被生育後嘅結果，如果從來都冇出世，&ldquo;你&rdquo;係唔會成為一個 capable of free will 嘅個體，亦都唔係一個moral agent. <br />\n<br />\n被強迫成為一個moral agent 嘅compensation就係能夠自由思考，毋須有其他compensation."},{"pid":"6e1193dadea663d3833449d1692f9e922e97e8fe","tid":230861,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認為free will 嘅存在本身已經compensate咗被生育哩樣嘢。<br />\n<br />\nfree will 嘅存在係被生育後嘅結果，如果從來都冇出世，&ldquo;你&rdquo;係唔會成為一個 capable of free will 嘅個體，亦都唔係一個moral agent. <br />\n<br />\n被強迫成為一個moral agent 嘅compensation就係能夠自由思考，毋須有其他compensation.</blockquote><br />\n所以我唔認為上一代應該用&ldquo;尊敬&rdquo;去補償下一代。<br />\n<br />\n利申：好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80efcc2bd99bcf586260cfb361fcd218a9c5a41","tid":230861,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:52:03.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"15c7ac615612b656a6f416d6d7454e3acb579e31","tid":230861,"uid":114175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認為free will 嘅存在本身已經compensate咗被生育哩樣嘢。<br />\n<br />\nfree will 嘅存在係被生育後嘅結果，如果從來都冇出世，&ldquo;你&rdquo;係唔會成為一個 capable of free will 嘅個體，亦都唔係一個moral agent. <br />\n<br />\n被強迫成為一個moral agent 嘅compensation就係能夠自由思考，毋須有其他compensation.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打嘅高質回覆，其實你都講得好有道理，但可惜人類係無可能達到絕對free will，因為會被各種社會規模limited，其中一項就係敬老"}]}